snippet.title: NATURAL JUICE | Red Tender Coconut Sarbath | Healthy Juice Making in Village | Summer Health Drinks
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we make our village traditional sarbath juice with farm-fresh King Coconut! Tender Coconut water is most effective in summer season. King Coconut variant is a very rare variant than a normal coconut!

We add basil seeds and King coconut meat to make this juice as healthy drink! The taste is divine!

localized.title: NATURAL JUICE | Red Tender Coconut Sarbath | Healthy Juice Making in Village | Summer Health Drinks
localized.description:
Today in our village, we make our village traditional sarbath juice with farm-fresh King Coconut! Tender Coconut water is most effective in summer season. King Coconut variant is a very rare variant than a normal coconut!

We add basil seeds and King coconut meat to make this juice as healthy drink! The taste is divine!

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3765 - Tapu Proposes To Sonu At Lovers Park?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey

snippet.title: Oppenheimer | New Trailer
snippet.description:
Oppenheimer - Only In Theaters 7 21 23

Written and directed by Christopher Nolan, Oppenheimer is an IMAX¬Æ-shot epic thriller that thrusts audiences into the pulse-pounding paradox of the enigmatic man who must risk destroying the world in order to save it. 
 
The film stars Cillian Murphy as J. Robert Oppenheimer and Emily Blunt as his wife, biologist and botanist Katherine ‚ÄúKitty‚Äù Oppenheimer. Oscar¬Æ winner Matt Damon portrays General Leslie Groves Jr., director of the Manhattan Project, and Robert Downey, Jr. plays Lewis Strauss, a founding commissioner of the U.S. Atomic Energy Commission. 
 
Academy Award¬Æ nominee Florence Pugh plays psychiatrist Jean Tatlock, Benny Safdie plays theoretical physicist Edward Teller, Michael Angarano plays Robert Serber and Josh Hartnett plays pioneering American nuclear scientist Ernest Lawrence.
 
Oppenheimer also stars Oscar¬Æ winner Rami Malek and reunites Nolan with eight-time Oscar¬Æ nominated actor, writer and filmmaker Kenneth Branagh. 
 
The cast includes Dane DeHaan (Valerian and the City of a Thousand Planets), Dylan Arnold (Halloween franchise), David Krumholtz (The Ballad of Buster Scruggs), Alden Ehrenreich (Solo: A Star Wars Story) and Matthew Modine (The Dark Knight Rises). 
 
The film is based on the Pulitzer Prize-winning book American Prometheus: The Triumph and Tragedy of J. Robert Oppenheimer by Kai Bird and the late Martin J. Sherwin. The film is produced by Emma Thomas, Atlas Entertainment‚Äôs Charles Roven and Christopher Nolan. 

Oppenheimer is filmed in a combination of IMAX¬Æ 65mm and 65mm large-format film photography including, for the first time ever, sections in IMAX¬Æ black and white analogue photography. 

Nolan‚Äôs films, including Tenet, Dunkirk, Interstellar, Inception and The Dark Knight trilogy, have earned more than $5 billion at the global box office and have been awarded 11 Oscars and 36 nominations, including two Best Picture nominations.

snippet.title: ‡§Æ‡•á‡§ó ‡•® (Meg 2) ‚Äì Official Hindi Trailer
snippet.description:
‡§µ‡•ã ‡§≤‡•å‡§ü ‡§Ü‡§è ‡§π‡•à‡§Ç ‡§¶‡•ã‡§¨‡§æ‡§∞‡§æ‡•§ ‡§¶‡•á‡§ñ‡§ø‡§Ø‡•á '‡§Æ‡•á‡§ó ‡•®' ‡§ï‡§æ ‡§π‡§ø‡§Ç‡§¶‡•Ä ‡§ü‡•ç‡§∞‡•á‡§≤‡§∞‡•§ ‡§Ü ‡§∞‡§π‡•Ä ‡§π‡•à ‡§Ü‡§™‡§ï‡•á ‡§®‡•õ‡§¶‡•Ä‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§∏‡§ø‡§®‡•á‡§Æ‡§æ‡§ò‡§∞‡•ã‡§Ç ‡§Æ‡•á‡§Ç ‡§Ö‡§ó‡§∏‡•ç‡§§ ‡•™ ‡§∏‡•á‡•§ #Meg2 starring Jason Statham in English, Hindi, Tamil & Telugu.

Get ready for the ultimate adrenaline rush this summer in ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench,‚Äù a literally larger-than-life thrill ride that supersizes the 2018 blockbuster and takes the action to higher heights and even greater depths with multiple massive Megs and so much more! Dive into uncharted waters with Jason Statham and global action icon Wu Jing as they lead a daring research team on an exploratory dive into the deepest depths of the ocean. Their voyage spirals into chaos when a malevolent mining operation threatens their mission and forces them into a high-stakes battle for survival. Pitted against colossal Megs and relentless environmental plunderers, our heroes must outrun, outsmart, and outswim their merciless predators in a pulse-pounding race against time. Immerse yourself in the most electrifying cinematic experience of the year with ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench‚Äù ‚Äì where the depths of the ocean are matched only by the heights of sheer, unstoppable excitement! 

Website: www.warnerbros-india.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WarnerBrosIndia
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/warnerbrosindia
Twitter: https://twitter.com/warnerbrosindia

Warner Bros. Pictures and CMC Pictures present ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench,‚Äù with Statham and Jing headlining an ensemble cast that also includes Sophia Cai (‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), Page Kennedy (‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), Sergio Peris-Mencheta (‚ÄúRambo: Last Blood‚Äù), Skyler Samuels (‚ÄúThe Gifted‚Äù), Sienna Guillory (‚ÄúResident Evil‚Äù films), and Cliff Curtis (‚ÄúAvatar‚Äù franchise). 

‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench‚Äù is directed by Ben Wheatley (‚ÄúIn the Earth,‚Äù ‚ÄúFree Fire‚Äù), from a screenplay by Jon Hoeber & Erich Hoeber (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts‚Äù) and Dean Georgaris (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúLara Croft: Tomb Raider ‚Äì The Cradle of Life‚Äù), and a screen story by Dean Georgaris and Jon Hoeber & Erich Hoeber, based on the novel The Trench by Steve Alten. The film is produced by Lorenzo di Bonaventura (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù) and Belle Avery (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúBefore the Devil Knows You‚Äôre Dead‚Äù), and executive produced by Jason Statham, Cate Adams, Ruigang Li, Catherine Xujun Ying, Wu Jing, E. Bennett Walsh, Erik Howsam, Randy Greenberg and Gerald R. Molen. 

Joining director Wheatley behind the camera are director of photography Haris Zambarloukous (‚ÄúBelfast,‚Äù ‚ÄúMurder on the Orient Express‚Äù), production designer Chris Lowe (‚ÄúThe Gray Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúNo Time to Die‚Äù) and editor Jonathan Amos (‚ÄúBaby Driver,‚Äù ‚ÄúPaddington 2‚Äù). The visual effects supervisor is Pete Bebb (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them,‚Äù ‚ÄúInception‚Äù), and costume designer is Lindsay Pugh (‚ÄúThe Matrix Resurrections,‚Äù ‚ÄúKrypton‚Äù). The music is by Harry Gregson-Williams (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Martian‚Äù). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and CMC Pictures present, in association with DF Pictures, a di Bonaventura/Apelles Entertainment, Inc. production, a Ben Wheatley film, ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in cinemas in India on August 4, 2023.

#WarnerBrosIndia #Meg2HindiTrailer

snippet.title: Middle Class Trap | Are You Actually Middle Class? Sandeep Maheshwari in Hindi
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

snippet.title: Moment former Pakistan PM Imran Khan is arrested
snippet.description:
Imran Khan, the former prime minister of Pakistan, has been arrested by the military as he appeared in court in Islamabad to face charges in a corruption case. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ‚ñ∫ http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

Fawad Chaudhry, a senior official with Khan‚Äôs Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf party, said the 72-year-old was arrested on Tuesday by agents from the National Accountability Bureau, the country‚Äôs anti-corruption body. A Reuters witness said that shortly after Khan entered through the gate of the Islamabad high court, contingents of paramilitary forces and armoured personnel carriers entered after him.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3765 - 8 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 37645: Tapu Ka Proposal
--------------------------------------------------------
The parents of a girl named Sonu come to see Bhide and tell him how their daughter eloped with her boyfriend. Bhide is anxious about Sonu because of this. When Madhavi receives a call from Anjali informing her of the Mahila Mandali meeting, she makes haste there. Bhide is instructed to wait since Madhavi is expecting a significant mango delivery. Sonu doesn't answer the phone when Bhide tries to call her, so he sets out to find her. Bhide eventually makes it to Lover's Park, where he sees Tapu bending over and giving Sonu a red rose. Follow along to discover more!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3765, 8 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

When Madhavi receives a call from Anjali informing her of the Mahila Mandali meeting, she makes haste there. Bhide is instructed to wait since Madhavi is expecting a significant mango delivery. Sonu doesn't answer the phone when Bhide tries to call her, so he sets out to find her. Bhide eventually makes it to Lover's Park, where he sees Tapu bending over and giving Sonu a red rose. Follow along to discover more!

snippet.title: Why is Manipur violence dangerous for India? | Manipur riots explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, we will explore the causes and consequences of the 2023 Manipur violence, an ongoing ethnic clash between the Hindu Meitei people and Christian tribal Kuki people in India‚Äôs north-eastern state of Manipur. The violence erupted on 3 May 2023 during the ‚ÄúTribal Solidarity March‚Äù called by the All Tribal Student Union Manipur (ATSUM) to protest the granting of reservations to the majority Meitei community1. The violence killed at least 60 people, and injured at least a further 230. It also resulted in the burning of 25 churches and the displacement of 23,000 people. The Indian Army and the Assam Rifles were deployed to restore law and order, and a shoot-at-sight order was issued in some areas. Internet services were also suspended for five days. We will examine the historical and political background of the conflict, which involves land rights, religious differences, and identity politics. We will also look at the current situation and the prospects for peace and reconciliation in this volatile region.

Please like, share, and subscribe to our channel for more videos on current affairs and social issues. Thank you for watching!

#Manipur #NorthEast #abhiandniyu

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

About Us:
Abhi and Niyu is the fastest growing Indian educational YouTube channel. Abhi and Niyu are a husband-wife couple who believe in the power of our youth.

Abhi and Niyu started their page to talk about positive, impactful ideas and to inspire offline action from online content. It was a way to change the way our negative feeds operated and replace negative news with positive, action-oriented news that made some change. They decode and simplify issues for Millenials and believe small steps lead to big outcomes in the future. Their videos span different genres like history, environment, and sustainability, policy discussions, social commentary, economics, personal finance, among others.

snippet.title: Shub-Man is now Spider-Man | Pavitr Prabhakar in Spider-Man: Across the SpiderVerse | June 2nd
snippet.description:
Thrilled to have the talented Shubman Gill as the voice of our very own - Indian Spider-Man, Pavitr Prabhakar in Spider-Man: Across the #SpiderVerse. 
Trailer dropping soon! Get ready for some web-slinging action! üï∑Ô∏èüáÆüá≥

Releasing in 10 languages all through the country; in English, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Punjabi, Gujarati, Marathi, Bengali, Kannada & Malayalam üï∏Ô∏è

Miles Morales returns for the next chapter of the Oscar¬Æ-winning Spider-Verse saga, Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse. After reuniting with Gwen Stacy, Brooklyn‚Äôs full-time, friendly neighborhood Spider-Man is catapulted across the Multiverse, where he encounters a team of Spider-People charged with protecting its very existence. But when the heroes clash on how to handle a new threat, Miles finds himself pitted against the other Spiders and must redefine what it means to be a hero so he can save the people he loves most.

snippet.description:

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 01 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Nimra Khan - 8th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :

Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela

en.description:
The Hindenburg Disaster of 1937 was a tragic accident caused by the world's largest airship built by the Zeppelin Company. It's one of the most iconic incidents that have happened in the world. The disaster claimed the lives of 36 people and marked the end of the era of passenger air travel. The cause of the fire is still unknown, although it is believed to have been sparked by a combination of static electricity and a hydrogen leak. But what was the full story of this accident? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee to find out!

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

Yakeen NEET 2.0 Batch Details : 

- Complete NEET Syllabus will be covered.
- We will cover Physics, Chemistry, Botany and Zoology.
- Two set of faculties will take the classes parallel in this batch.
- Both set of faculties will take live classes in this batch.

- Peer to Peer doubt solving will be provided.
- Classes starting from 18th May 2023
- Syllabus will end by 10th March 2024.
- The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2024 Exams

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3764 - 6 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3764: Jasoos Bhide
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide begins to have concerns about Tapu's motivations and makes the decision to keep an eye on him. Bhide gets into an auto and instructs the driver to keep driving in the same direction as Tapu and Sonu's vehicle. Bhide tries to bribe the vehicle driver after he refuses to obey his commands. When Tapu and Sonu are finally spotted entering a shrine, Bhide follows them as well. Bhide runs across one of his student's parents at the temple's stairs and strikes up a conversation with him. Bhide becomes impatient because it has caused a significant diversion from his stalking. See how Bhide flees when he is going to be caught by Tapu and Sonu in the act by watching the episode!

snippet.description:
Bhide begins to have concerns about Tapu's motivations and makes the decision to keep an eye on him. Bhide gets into an auto and instructs the driver to keep driving in the same direction as Tapu and Sonu's vehicle. Bhide tries to bribe the vehicle driver after he refuses to obey his commands. When Tapu and Sonu are finally spotted entering a shrine, Bhide follows them as well. Bhide runs across one of his student's parents at the temple's stairs and strikes up a conversation with him. Bhide becomes impatient because it has caused a significant diversion from his stalking. See how Bhide flees when he is going to be caught by Tapu and Sonu in the act by watching the episode!

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Sakhiye Saheliye (Official) | Godday Godday Chaa | Sonam Bajwa | Tania | Jasmeen | V Rakx Music
snippet.description:
Tips Industries Ltd and Tips Punjabi presents the new Punjabi Song "Sakhiye Saheliye" is from the upcoming movie Godday Godday Chaa. The song is sung by Jasmeen Akhtar, with lyrics penned by Harinder Kour and music composed by Rakesh Raxx. The music video features Sonam Bajwa, Tania, Gitaj Bindrakhia and Gurjazz.

Movie Releasing Worldwide On 26th May 2023.

#sonambajwa #jasmeenakthar #sakhiyesaheliye #gitajbindrakhia #goddaygoddaychaa #tania #newpunjabisong

Sakhiye Saheliye Lyrics:

Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sajaa...
Naviye naveliye,
Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khaban vale raah....
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sajaa.
Akhan asmaan vall chuk k tan vekhiye,
Kandhan kaule shattan kolo shutt k tan vekhiye,
Dhup shan de utte haq rakh k tan vekhiye,
Aaja aaja layiye geet zindagi de gaa...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sjaa....
Kandhan kaule, shattan kolon shutt kithe jaavana,
Murh k tan panchi ne aahlane ch aavana,
Ghuggian ne bahuta uchi sikhea na gaavana,
Buk k bathere sanu zindagi de chaa,
Naviye naveliye,
Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khabaan vaale raah....
Kholiye jo band pyi khaban di kitab ni,
Haasyean di rutt vala mangiye hisaab ni,
Saukhe ne swaal par aukhe ne jwaab ni,
Nehrean nu deyiye jaag chananan da laa..
Sakhiye Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sjaa....
Suk gye baghan vichon labhna ko jhalliye,
Hukaman ch rahiye bas hukaman ch chaliye,
Chappa k zameen pairan heth jo swalliye,
Nadiyan ne muk jana vich dariya...
Naviye naveliye,

Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khabaan vaale raah....
Duniya de ranga vich apna v rang hove,
Ajj hoyie kathe fr apna eh kal hove...
Reeta te riwaaz nve ghad lvange,
Dha  k purana raag nva lyie gaa...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Naviye naveliye.
Sakhiye saheliye...
Hath farh mera lyie kafila bna,
Khat k lea de sanu nikke Nike chah,
Gujiye paheliye,
Chandan di galiye...
Fikara nu deyie fook maar k udha,
Sanu v tan thode khamb kholne Sikha...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye...
Mathe utte lyie chan sooraj sjaa...
Hath farh mera lyie qaafila bna,
Fikara nu deyie fook maar k udha...
Naviye naveliye,
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,

Ek hath reejhan saade ek hath chaa,
Udh jana asi khamb chuni de bna,
Dharti te pair ajj nahio lgda,
Amber v hoyea neeva neeva lgda,
Asin duniya gulaabi rang laini e ranga...

snippet.title: Manipur: Govt issues 'shoot at sight' orders as violence flares; 9,000 people rescued
snippet.description:
The #manipur  government has issued "shoot at sight" orders as violence in the state spread to its capital Imphal. Security has been strengthened, with the deployment of 55 army columns. The Rapid Action Force has been flown in. Around 500 personnel of the Rapid Action Force, a riot control police, have been flown in. More than 9,000 people have been rescued from violence-hit areas by the security forces.
